folder: Tremont Avenue (East & Hughes Avenue, Bronx, NY
text:
East Tremont Ave., east from Hughes Ave. Also shown is a general view as seen from the Bergen Building, at the S.E. corner of Arthur Ave.
May 1926.
Brown Brothers.
Neg E L-453

folder: Hughes Avenue & Tremont Avenue (East), Bronx, NY
text:
Hughes Ave., north from East Tremont Ave. Also shown is a general view northeastward of the East Tremont section of the Bronx as seen from the Bergen Building, st the S.E. corner of East Tremont and Arthur Aves.
May 1926.
Brown Brothers.
